articles.author: Hilary Whiteman
articles.title: Woman survives snake bite during days lost in Australia’s Snowy Mountains - CNN
articles.description: A woman who went missing on a solo hike in Australia’s Snowy Mountains was found “dazed and injured” on Sunday, police said, after suffering a suspected snake bite while missing for nearly two weeks.
